{
  "stem": "3002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was married there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My younger sister was too young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my older sister was also married in the east.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my, and my, and my youngest sister, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all-- my other brother was married there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister was married there, too, and my other brother was married there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wanted me to run towards them, to the east.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I got in touch with my friend in Przedborz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He really looked at-- he had the look of a real Polack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was tall, blond, blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we decided to just, to take a step.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We two should run towards my other part of the family, there on the east.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We took off the stars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We went by train, towards the east.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember which station so which-- how far--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at that time, no papers at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just went on the sheer luck that nobody will recognize us as Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And first we traveled by train towards the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at that time, wasn't so easy because the trains, you didn't take one train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to take one train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then get off, and wait a long time to take another train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in between, there were just Poles snooping around to smell out if there's any Jew on the station which was hiding or running.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they just passed us by.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We made it to the border, and that was already wintertime.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Through the border, he had-- there were some smugglers who would smuggle people to the east.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we had to go in snow, by foot, over the border.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When we reached the last station by train, we had to go over the border by foot.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
